<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mayoor Ahmad Dar | Data Analyst</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --surface-color: #1e293b;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --accent: #3b82f6;
            --accent-hover: #2563eb;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1.5rem 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 2rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Sections */
        section {
            padding: 6rem 5%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 0;
            width: 50%;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        #hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding-top: 5rem;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-content h3 {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border: 1px solid var(--text-muted);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .hero-image {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: var(--surface-color);
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            border: 1px dashed var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* About */
        #about p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        /* Skills */
        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .skill-category {
            background: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .skill-category h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .skill-item {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .skill-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .progress {
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        /* Projects */
        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tag {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .project-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        /* Experience Timeline */
        .timeline {
            border-left: 2px solid var(--surface-color);
            padding-left: 2rem;
            margin-left: 1rem;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -35px;
            top: 5px;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .timeline-date {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .timeline-item h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .timeline-item ul {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .timeline-item li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Education */
        .edu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .edu-card {
            background: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .edu-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .edu-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Contact */
        #contact {
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .contact-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .contact-info a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--surface-color);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        textarea {
            height: 150px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .cta-text {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            #hero {
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 3rem;
            }
            .hero-image {
                display: none;
            }
            .contact-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            nav {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">M.A. DAR</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
            <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
            <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
            <a href="#education">Education</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Mayoor Ahmad Dar</h1>
            <h3>Economics-Trained Data Analyst</h3>
            <p>Turning Data into Business Decisions. MSc Economics at FAU Erlangen-Nürnberg.</p>
            <div>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Download CV</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Me</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            [Professional Photo Placeholder]
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>I am an economics student who looks at data differently. I don't just see rows and columns; I see human behavior, market inefficiencies, and business opportunities. My training in economics grounds my technical skills in real-world logic.</p>
        <p>While many analysts focus purely on the code, my priority is the outcome. I bridge the gap between complex statistical models and actionable business strategy, ensuring that data isn't just processed, but actually understood and utilized by stakeholders.</p>
        <p>Currently based in Germany and pursuing my Master's at FAU Erlangen-Nürnberg, I am actively seeking working student or internship roles where I can apply my analytical rigor to solve tangible business problems.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
        <h2>Technical & Business Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
            <div class="skill-category">
                <h3>Data Analytics</h3>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>Excel (Advanced)</span><span>90%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 90%"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>Power BI</span><span>85%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 85%"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>SQL</span><span>70%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 70%"></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-category">
                <h3>Statistical Tools</h3>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>STATA</span><span>80%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 80%"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>MATLAB</span><span>75%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 75%"></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-category">
                <h3>Business & Languages</h3>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>Economic Modeling</span><span>85%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 85%"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>MS Office Suite</span><span>95%</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 95%"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div class="skill-info"><span>German (B1)</span><span>Proficient for Work</span></div>
                    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress" style="width: 60%"></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="projects-grid">
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Retail Sales Analysis Dashboard</h3>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">Excel</span>
                    <span class="tag">Pivot Tables</span>
                </div>
                <p>Analyzed multi-region German retail data using advanced formulas and pivot tables to extract regional revenue insights and identify underperforming sectors.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-align: center;">View Project</a>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>E-Commerce Sales Dashboard</h3>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">Power BI</span>
                    <span class="tag">DAX</span>
                    <span class="tag">Power Query</span>
                </div>
                <p>Developed an interactive dashboard utilizing Power Query and DAX measures to track critical KPI cards and visualize real-time sales velocity.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-align: center;">View Project</a>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Fiscal Policy Impact Analysis</h3>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">STATA</span>
                    <span class="tag">Econometrics</span>
                </div>
                <p>Conducted regression analysis on Indian budget data. Built econometric models to isolate variables and present concrete research findings on policy effectiveness.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-align: center;">View Project</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="experience">
        <h2>Experience</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">July 2024 — March 2025</div>
                <h3>Data Analyst Intern</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--accent);">E-Max India</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Designed and maintained Power BI dashboards for real-time KPI tracking across departments.</li>
                    <li>Automated reporting workflows, reducing manual data entry and formatting effort by 40%.</li>
                    <li>Established structured data documentation and reporting governance protocols to ensure data integrity.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="education">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div class="edu-grid">
            <div class="edu-card">
                <h3>MSc Economics</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem;">FAU Erlangen-Nürnberg</p>
                <p>October 2025 — Present</p>
            </div>
            <div class="edu-card">
                <h3>BA Honours Economics</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Cluster University of Srinagar</p>
                <p>2021 — 2024</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Grade: 8.0 / 10</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <div class="contact-container">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> &nbsp; <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com">your.email@example.com</a></p>
                <p><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> &nbsp; <a href="#">linkedin.com/in/yourprofile</a></p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> &nbsp; Nuremberg, Germany</p>
                <div class="cta-text">Open to Working Student Roles in Data Analysis.</div>
            </div>
            <form id="contactForm" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Form submission ready to be connected to a backend like Formspree.');">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                <textarea placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>